    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but i've already looked into it and i dont really have time to go to the doctor for every little thing. i'm just trying to be proactive with my health. if my blood feels fine and i have no symptoms, wouldn't a lower dose like 2mg just be a more natural way to maintain the balance without overdoing the chemicals? it seems like a logical step since i'm doing so well.",
