      "content": "i hear u on the risks but i'm just looking for some clarity. if i were to do it slowly, like taper down to 2mg over a week or so, would that be considered a safer way to transition? i just really feel like 5mg is overkill for me now since my lifestyle is so healthy. like, is there any actual medical reason why 2mg would be too low for someone in my position?",
